[SN]TITLE[SN]
First Orkney sexual abuse support service launched

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A dedicated service has been launched in Orkney for the first time to support people who been victims of rape or sexual abuse.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Orkney Rape Crisis will have a support worker available to provide information in the islands.
The support will also be available for appointments with doctors, police or at court.
The service will also give therapeutic help and work closely with other bodies to provide a range of support needs.
